00:14:22.640 --> 00:14:28.159
and learning. But the point that I make is, and I've got a copy of it right here, because I do

00:14:28.159 --> 00:14:35.599
this example all the time. That wasn't January of this year, that was January of 1961. That was

00:14:35.599 --> 00:14:41.840
Marvin Minsky in 1961, talking about reinforcement learning and pattern recognition, and everything

00:14:41.840 --> 00:14:48.080
that we are still working on today, over 60 years later. It's not to say that we haven't made some

00:14:48.080 --> 00:14:53.440
