00:47:12.879 --> 00:47:18.639
process in what's called set point regulation control, there's only one final destination that

00:47:18.639 --> 00:47:26.479
gets you that reward and you fail thousands of times more than you succeed. So failure is key

00:47:26.479 --> 00:47:31.840
